snippet.title: Aexia - Your  Gateway into VR Roleplaying.
snippet.description:
Welcome to Aexia, your gateway to VR roleplay. Meta Quest-friendly VR roleplays with no previous experience required. Discover—or perhaps rediscover—your passion for performing and roleplaying. Join our community of actors, storytellers, and introverted extroverts. You and your creativity are welcome here.

Join us on Discord for EARLY ACCESS: https://discord.com/invite/En4dMuJhFw

Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@aexiavr
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/aexiavr
Twitter - https://twitter.com/AexiaVR
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/aexiavr/
